# React Conventions

- Name files like components (ex: `SuperNavBar` -> `super-nav-bar.tsx`)
- Don't use `export default` use `export` (\*\*except when inside the `src/app` folder
  of expo)
- If exports many components use coumpound components pattern (ex: `MyNavBar.Header`)
- use tamagui
